{"chunk": "4.3.1 Gerarchia dei nomi\nLa struttura degli indirizzi definiti dal DNS e\u0300 strettamente gerarchica e si rappresenta come \nuna struttura ad albero di nodi, a ognuno dei quali e\u0300 associata un\u2019 etichetta . Al livello pi\u00f9 \nalto della gerarchia si trova la radice dell\u2019albero, denominata root , cui non e\u0300 associata alcuna \netichetta. Il primo livello dell\u2019albero al di sotto della radice comprende nodi indicati come", "embedding": [0.040160846, 0.044776533, -0.06671935, 0.03322075, 0.00030645993, 0.015258199, 0.06428966, -0.021977047, 0.06954606, 0.01743706, 0.0042721024, 0.02765507, 0.0063691214, -0.0010788995, 0.0044697006, -0.009218508, 0.12941785, 0.07328561, -0.009536349, 0.050353613, 0.01752954, -0.030990612, 0.037660986, 0.014926217, 0.0016110677, -0.0121022845, 0.03846712, 0.04630533, -0.010144669, 0.00607034, 0.08071948, 0.03144433, -0.03328529, 0.0030045449, -0.019768314, 0.023893936, 0.012105272, 0.010741319, -0.004022344, -0.008241115, -0.05462452, -0.019923568, -0.038016513, 0.05822557, 0.0045433156, -0.057524633, 0.051432136, 0.01345812, -0.069795705, 0.050967485, -0.0024674083, -0.019143566, -0.038909554, 0.061541434, 0.06973872, -0.012272924, -0.01950864, 0.009195192, -0.013687001, 0.007355385, -0.021335343, -0.037422158, -0.008192135, -0.028016405, 0.0075534857, 0.07056982, -0.02470636, -0.011188017, -0.0617864, 0.02864566, -0.034587495, 0.079571314, -0.019329457, -0.015267978, -0.018843891, 0.038555507, 0.029164707, -0.021584135, 0.016965088, 0.03348174, -0.0013799669, 0.026146943, -0.0031500084, -0.039944354, -0.036648404, 0.047283657, -0.024341037, -0.039730377, -0.030248107, -0.024798818, 0.064266786, 0.051436305, -0.056232784, -0.00080996647, -0.010097667, 0.011848626, -0.06668513, -0.088996895, 0.05953325, 0.099759325, 0.02576615, -0.005159881, 0.0075731995, -0.029209983, 0.030405749, -0.018062858, -0.04631217, -0.09718512, -0.009212845, 0.060869135, -0.00077906717, -0.028392803, 0.062336802, -0.020238